Which class is this? Instructors are not able to enroll students into classes. If there is space in the class, Michael-David Sasson can enroll students into CS classes and I can enroll students into EE/EECS classes.

It is possible the instructor is asking for your SID to share that information with one of us (or staff outside of EECS if relevant) to facilitate our ability to enroll you into the class.

If it is a non-EE/CS/EECS class, you will need to talk with that department.
